name: Isbel
content:
Isbel was a female Twi'lek smuggler who operated on Vreni Island on Corellia during the time of the Galactic Civil War.
Isbel was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Isbel was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
